290 
291  // Store the result.
292  wrapper::vstore(out_ptr + x, vout_8p0);

209  break;
210  case ActivationLayerInfo::ActivationFunction::SOFT_RELU:

317  auto mean = ScalarType(0.0);
318  auto var = ScalarType(0.0);
319  auto gamma = ScalarType(1.0);
320  auto beta = ScalarType(0.0);
321  auto dwc_bias_in_scalar = ScalarType(0.0);
322  execute_window_loop(
323  win,
324  [&](const Coordinates &id)
325  {
326  var = input_var[id[2]];
327  if (input_gamma != nullptr)
328  {
329  gamma = input_gamma[id[2]];
330  }
331 
332  if (id[1] == 0)
333  {
334  mean = input_mean[id[2]];
335 
336  // Construct vectors
337  mean_vec = wrapper::vdup_n(mean, ExactTagType{});
338  if (input_beta != nullptr)
339  {
340  beta = input_beta[id[2]];
341  beta_vec = wrapper::vdup_n(beta, ExactTagType{});
342  }

346  dwc_bias_in_scalar = dwc_bias_in[id[2]];
347  }
348

350  dwc_bias_out[id[2]] = (dwc_bias_tmp_scalar * gamma) + beta;
351  }
352 
353  int x = window_start_x;
354  auto dwc_w_in_ptr = reinterpret_cast<const ScalarType *>(dwc_w_in.ptr());
355  auto dwc_w_out_ptr = reinterpret_cast<ScalarType *>(dwc_w_out.ptr());
356  var_vec = wrapper::vdup_n(var, ExactTagType{});
357  gamma_vec = wrapper::vdup_n(gamma, ExactTagType{});
358  rvar_vec = wrapper::vinvsqrt(wrapper::vadd(var_vec, epsilon_vec));
359 
360  for (; x <= (window_end_x - window_step_x); x += window_step_x)
361  {
362  auto wn = wrapper::vloadq(dwc_w_in_ptr + x);
363  wn = wrapper::vmul(wn, rvar_vec);
364  wn = wrapper::vmul(wn, gamma_vec);
365 
366  // Store results
367  wrapper::vstore(dwc_w_out_ptr + x, wn);
368  }
369 
370  // Compute left-over elements
371  for (; x < window_end_x; ++x)
372  {
373  *(dwc_w_out_ptr + x) = *(dwc_w_in_ptr + x) / std::sqrt(var + ScalarType(epsilon)) * gamma;
374  }
375  },
376  dwc_w_in, dwc_w_out);
377 }

270  tmp_f = 1.f / (1.f + std::exp(-tmp_f));
271  tmp = quantize_qasymm8(tmp_f, qi_out);
272  }
273 #endif // __aarch64__
274  else if (act == ActivationLayerInfo::ActivationFunction::TANH)
275  {
276  float tmp_f = dequantize_qasymm8(in, qi_in);
277  tmp_f = a_f32 * std::tanh(b_f32 * tmp_f);
278  tmp = quantize_qasymm8(tmp_f, qi_out);
279  }
280 #ifndef __aarch64__ // LUT-based implementation is used for aarch64 instead.
281  else if (act == ActivationLayerInfo::ActivationFunction::HARD_SWISH)
282  {
283  float tmp_f = dequantize_qasymm8(in, qi_in);
284  tmp_f = tmp_f * ((std::min(std::max((tmp_f + 3), 0.0f), 6.0f)) * 0.166666667f);
285  tmp = quantize_qasymm8(tmp_f, qi_out);
286  }
287  else if (act == ActivationLayerInfo::ActivationFunction::LEAKY_RELU)
288  {
289  float tmp_f = dequantize_qasymm8(in, qi_in);
290  tmp_f = tmp_f > 0 ? tmp_f : tmp_f * a_f32;
291  tmp = quantize_qasymm8(tmp_f, qi_out);
292  }
293  else if (act == ActivationLayerInfo::ActivationFunction::GELU)
294  {
295  float tmp_f = dequantize_qasymm8(in, qi_in);
296  tmp = tmp_f * 0.5f * (1.0f + std::erff(in / 1.41421356237f));
297  tmp = quantize_qasymm8(tmp_f, qi_out);
298  }
299 #endif // __aarch64__
300  else
301  {
302  ARM_COMPUTE_ERROR("Unsupported activation function");
303  }
304  *(output_ptr + x) = tmp;
305  }
306  },
307  input, output);
308 }

211  else
212  {
213  ARM_COMPUTE_ERROR("Unsupported activation function");
214  }
215  wrapper::vstore(output_ptr + x, tmp);
216  }
217 
218  // Compute left-over elements
219  for (; x < window_end_x; ++x)
220  {
221  qasymm8_signed_t in = *(reinterpret_cast<const qasymm8_signed_t *>(input_ptr + x));
222  qasymm8_signed_t tmp = 0;
223  if (act == ActivationLayerInfo::ActivationFunction::RELU)
224  {
225  tmp = std::max(const_0, in);
226  tmp = utility::clamp<int32_t, qasymm8_signed_t>(support::cpp11::lround(tmp * s + o));
227  }
228  else if (act == ActivationLayerInfo::ActivationFunction::BOUNDED_RELU)
229  {
230  tmp = std::min(a, std::max(const_0, in));
231  tmp = utility::clamp<int32_t, qasymm8_signed_t>(support::cpp11::lround(tmp * s + o));
232  }
233  else if (act == ActivationLayerInfo::ActivationFunction::LU_BOUNDED_RELU)
234  {
235  tmp = std::min(a, std::max(b, in));
236  tmp = utility::clamp<int32_t, qasymm8_signed_t>(support::cpp11::lround(tmp * s + o));
237  }
238 #ifndef __aarch64__ // LUT-based implementation is used for aarch64 instead.
239  else if (act == ActivationLayerInfo::ActivationFunction::LOGISTIC)
240  {
241  float tmp_f = dequantize_qasymm8_signed(in, qi_in);
242  tmp_f = 1.f / (1.f + std::exp(-tmp_f));
243  tmp = quantize_qasymm8_signed(tmp_f, qi_out);
244  }
245 #endif // __aarch64__
246  else if (act == ActivationLayerInfo::ActivationFunction::TANH)
247  {
248  float tmp_f = dequantize_qasymm8_signed(in, qi_in);
249  tmp_f = a_f32 * std::tanh(b_f32 * tmp_f);
250  tmp = quantize_qasymm8_signed(tmp_f, qi_out);
251  }
252  else if (act == ActivationLayerInfo::ActivationFunction::HARD_SWISH)
253  {
254  float tmp_f = dequantize_qasymm8_signed(in, qi_in);
255  tmp_f = tmp_f * ((std::min(std::max((tmp_f + 3), 0.0f), 6.0f)) * 0.166666667f);
256  tmp = quantize_qasymm8_signed(tmp_f, qi_out);
257  }
258  else if (act == ActivationLayerInfo::ActivationFunction::LEAKY_RELU)
259  {
260  float tmp_f = dequantize_qasymm8_signed(in, qi_in);
261  tmp_f = tmp_f > 0 ? tmp_f : tmp_f * a_f32;
262  tmp = quantize_qasymm8_signed(tmp_f, qi_out);
263  }
264  else
265  {
266  ARM_COMPUTE_ERROR("Unsupported activation function");
267  }
268  *(output_ptr + x) = tmp;
269  }
270  },
271  input, output);
272 }

134  vec_elements_flt.val[1] = vexpq_f32(vmulq_f32(vec_elements_flt.val[1], scale_beta_vec));
135  vec_elements_flt.val[2] = vexpq_f32(vmulq_f32(vec_elements_flt.val[2], scale_beta_vec));
136  vec_elements_flt.val[3] = vexpq_f32(vmulq_f32(vec_elements_flt.val[3], scale_beta_vec));
137  vec_sum.val[0] = vaddq_f32(vec_sum.val[0], vec_elements_flt.val[0]);
138  vec_sum.val[1] = vaddq_f32(vec_sum.val[1], vec_elements_flt.val[1]);
139  vec_sum.val[2] = vaddq_f32(vec_sum.val[2], vec_elements_flt.val[2]);
140  vec_sum.val[3] = vaddq_f32(vec_sum.val[3], vec_elements_flt.val[3]);
141  }
142 
143  vst4q_f32(tmp_ptr + x, vec_elements_flt);
144  }
145 
146  /* Reduce sum */
147  const float32x4_t sum_16_byte =
148  vaddq_f32(vaddq_f32(vec_sum.val[0], vec_sum.val[1]), vaddq_f32(vec_sum.val[2], vec_sum.val[3]));
149 
150  float sum;
151 
152 #ifdef __aarch64__
153  sum = wrapper::vaddv(sum_16_byte);
154 #else // __aarch64__
155  auto sum_res = vpadd_f32(vget_high_f32(sum_16_byte), vget_low_f32(sum_16_byte));
156  sum_res = vpadd_f32(sum_res, sum_res);
157  sum = wrapper::vgetlane(sum_res, 0);
158 #endif // __aarch64__
159 
160  /* Run remaining elements */
161  for (; x < input_width; ++x)
162  {
163  float element{};
164  if (IS_LOG)
165  {
166  element = (max_val - in_ptr[x]) * scale_beta;
167  sum += std::exp(element);
168  }
169  else
170  {
171  element = std::exp((max_val - in_ptr[x]) * scale_beta);
172  sum += element;
173  }
174 
175  tmp_ptr[x] = element;
176  }
177 
178  if (!IS_LOG)
179  {
180  sum_transformed = 256.f / sum;
181  }
182  else
183  {
184  sum_transformed = std::log(sum);
185  }
186  } // Compute exponentials and sum
187 
188  /* Normalize exponentials */
189  {
190  constexpr bool is_qasymm8_signed = std::is_same<T, qasymm8_signed_t>::value;
191 
192  const float32x4_t sum_vec = vdupq_n_f32(sum_transformed);
193 
194  /* Loop over row and compute softmax */
195  int x = 0;
196  for (; x <= (input_width - vec_size); x += vec_size)
197  {
198  using int_vec_type = wrapper::traits::neon_vector_t<T, 16>;
199  float32x4x4_t vec_in = vld4q_f32(tmp_ptr + x);
200  int_vec_type normalized_value{};
201  if (IS_LOG)
202  {
203  const float32x4x4_t sub = {
204  vsubq_f32(vec_in.val[0], sum_vec),
205  vsubq_f32(vec_in.val[1], sum_vec),
206  vsubq_f32(vec_in.val[2], sum_vec),
207  vsubq_f32(vec_in.val[3], sum_vec),
208  };
209  normalized_value = convert_float_to_int<float32x4x4_t, int_vec_type>(sub);
210  }
211  else
212  {
213  float32x4x4_t mul = {
214  vmulq_f32(vec_in.val[0], sum_vec),
215  vmulq_f32(vec_in.val[1], sum_vec),
216  vmulq_f32(vec_in.val[2], sum_vec),
217  vmulq_f32(vec_in.val[3], sum_vec),
218  };
219 
220  if (is_qasymm8_signed)
221  {
222  const auto offset_vec = wrapper::vdup_n(128.f, wrapper::traits::vector_128_tag{});
223  mul.val[0] = wrapper::vsub(mul.val[0], offset_vec);
224  mul.val[1] = wrapper::vsub(mul.val[1], offset_vec);
225  mul.val[2] = wrapper::vsub(mul.val[2], offset_vec);
226  mul.val[3] = wrapper::vsub(mul.val[3], offset_vec);
227  }
228 
229  normalized_value = convert_float_to_int<float32x4x4_t, int_vec_type>(mul);
230  }
231  wrapper::vstore(out_ptr + x, normalized_value);
232  }
233  /* Run remaining elements */
234  for (; x < input_width; ++x)
235  {
236  if (IS_LOG)
237  {
238  out_ptr[x] = utils::cast::saturate_cast<T>(tmp_ptr[x] - sum_transformed);
239  }
240  else
241  {
242  out_ptr[x] = utils::cast::saturate_cast<T>((tmp_ptr[x] * sum_transformed) -
243  (is_qasymm8_signed ? 128.f : 0));
244  }
245  }
246  } // Normalize exponentials
247  },
248  in_it, out_it);
249 }

70  }
71  float s = qi_in.scale / qi_out.scale;
72  float o = -qi_in.offset * s + qi_out.offset;
73  auto vs = svdup_n_f32(s);
74  auto vo = svdup_n_f32(o);

77  const auto voffset_in = svdup_n_s32(qi_in.offset);

104  if (act == ActivationLayerInfo::ActivationFunction::RELU)
105  {

108  // Re-quantize to new output space
109  tmp = requant ? svmla_qasymm8_z(pg, tmp, vs, vo) : tmp;
110  }
111  else if (act == ActivationLayerInfo::ActivationFunction::BOUNDED_RELU)
112  {
113  // Perform activation
114  tmp = svmin_u8_z(pg, va, svmax_u8_z(pg, vconst_0, vin));

122  // Re-quantize to new output space

124  }
125  else if (act == ActivationLayerInfo::ActivationFunction::LOGISTIC)

146  }

148  {
149  // De-quantize

160  }

193  // Re-quantize to new output space
194  tmp = svquantize_signed_z(pg, tmp_dep, qi_out);
195  }

219  p3 = svcmpgt_s32(pg, svget4_s32(vin_s32, 3), voffset_in);
